{"word":"G375 - ἀναπέμπω - anapémpō - an-ap-em'-po - Send","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀναπέμπω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">anapémpō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">an-ap-em'-po</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Send</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - அனுப்பு"},{"paragraph":"to send up, to send back"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G303 - ἀνά - aná - an-ah'/303\">G303</a> and <a href=\"#/G3992 - πέμπω - pémpō - pem'-po/3992\">G3992</a>; to <i>send up</i> or <i>back:</i> - send (again).</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}